summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Engineer to incur an indebtedness against the General Fund of the City of Seattle in the sum of Fifteen Thousand Two Hundred Forty-eight and 93/100 Dollars ($15,248.93), on account of the cost and expense of the improvement of 32nd Avenue et al, by paving the same, as authorized by Ordinance No. 19846, creating Local Improvement District No. 1928.
